# =============================================================================
# AI AGENT IGNORE FILE - ZeroClaw Project
# =============================================================================
# This file specifies files and directories that AI agents should ignore
# to reduce token consumption and focus on relevant code.
#
# Usage:
# - Claude: Add to .clinerules or reference in CLAUDE.md
# - GitHub Copilot: Add patterns to .gitignore (already supported)
# - Other agents: Load this file and respect the patterns
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# 1. INTERNATIONALIZATION (i18n) - Non-English Translations Only
# =============================================================================
# User only needs English (en) - ignoring all other language translations

# Greek translations
docs/i18n/el/

# French translations
docs/i18n/fr/

# Japanese translations
docs/i18n/ja/

# Russian translations
docs/i18n/ru/

# Vietnamese translations
docs/i18n/vi/

# Chinese Simplified translations
docs/i18n/zh-CN/

# Language summary files (non-English)
docs/SUMMARY.el.md
docs/SUMMARY.fr.md
docs/SUMMARY.ja.md
docs/SUMMARY.ru.md
docs/SUMMARY.vi.md
docs/SUMMARY.zh-CN.md

# Vietnamese-specific docs
docs/commands-reference.vi.md
docs/config-reference.vi.md
docs/troubleshooting.vi.md
docs/one-click-bootstrap.vi.md
docs/vi/

# Chinese-specific docs outside i18n tree
docs/security/advisory-maintainer-checklist.zh-CN.md
docs/security/advisory-metadata-template.zh-CN.md
docs/security/private-vulnerability-report-template.zh-CN.md

# Root-level non-English docs
CONTRIBUTING.el.md

